headline: ClearBridge Appreciation Strategy Q2 2025 Commentary
summary: The ClearBridge Appreciation Strategy underperformed the benchmark S&P 500 Index in the second quarter. On an absolute basis, the Strategy had gains in seven of 11 sectors.
